P=_1sp_RG796_Select             |              |@per D,@p1 C(9),@p2 C(9),@p3 N(14,2) O  |Select @p3=SP800 from RG796 where PERIOD=@per AND SP797=@p1 AND SP1630=@p2
#
#===============================================================================
#==PROCEDURE EscalateTLock
# Name                          |Descr         |Parameters                              |Source                                                                          
P=_1sp_RA796_TLock              |EscalateTLock |                                        |set nocount on declare @i integer select @i=1 from RA796(TABLOCK HOLDLOCK) where 0=1
#
#===============================================================================
