P=_1sp_RG2716_Change            |              |@per D,@p1 C(9),@p2 C(9),@p3 C(9),@p4 C(13),@p5 N(14,3)|{\
Set Nocount On
Update RG2716
  set SP2720=Case When ABS(SP2720+@p5)>99999999999.999 Then 99999999999.999 Else SP2720+@p5 End
  where PERIOD=@per AND SP2717=@p1 AND SP2718=@p2 AND SP2719=@p3 AND SP3411=@p4
