P=_1sp_RG4118_TLockX            |EscalateTLockX|                                        |set nocount on declare @i integer select @i=1 from RG4118(TABLOCKX HOLDLOCK) where 0=1
#
#===============================================================================
#==TABLE no 652    : Регистр Акт
# Name    |Descr                         |SQLTableNam|RecordLock
T=RG4118  |Регистр Акт                   |RG4118     |          
#-----Fields-------
# Name                  |Descr               |Type|Length|Precision
F=PERIOD                |Period Registr      |D   |0     |0        
F=SP4121                |(P)Договор          |C   |13    |0        
F=SP4137                |(P)Годы             |N   |4     |0        
F=SP4119                |(P)Месяцы           |C   |9     |0        
F=SP4141                |(P)Док              |C   |13    |0        
F=SP4120                |(P)Количество       |N   |10    |0        
#----Indexes------
# Name                           |Descr         |Unique|Indexed fields                                              |Type       
I=PK_RG4118                      |PERIOD+PROP   |1     |PERIOD,SP4121,SP4137,SP4119,SP4141                          |1          
#
#===============================================================================
#==PROCEDURE 
# Name                          |Descr         |Parameters                              |Source                                                                          
P=_1sp_RG4118_Change            |              |@per D,@p1 C(13),@p2 N(4),@p3 C(9),@p4 C(13),@p5 N(10)|{\
Set Nocount On
Update RG4118
  set SP4120=Case When ABS(SP4120+@p5)>9999999999 Then 9999999999 Else SP4120+@p5 End
  where PERIOD=@per AND SP4121=@p1 AND SP4137=@p2 AND SP4119=@p3 AND SP4141=@p4
if @@ROWCOUNT=0
    insert into RG4118 values(@per,@p1,@p2,@p3,@p4,@p5)
\}
