P=_1sp_RG4625_Select            |              |@per D,@p1 C(9),@p2 C(9),@p3 C(9),@p4 C(9),@p5 C(9),@p6 N(14,3) O,@p7 N(14,4) O,@p8 N(14,4) O|Select @p6=SP4624,@p7=SP6762,@p8=SP6763 from RG4625 where PERIOD=@per AND SP6758=@p1 AND SP6759=@p2 AND SP6760=@p3 AND SP6761=@p4 AND SP4622=@p5
#
