P=_1sp_RG4631_TLock             |EscalateTLock |                                        |set nocount on declare @i integer select @i=1 from RG4631(TABLOCK HOLDLOCK) where 0=1
#
#===============================================================================
#==PROCEDURE EscalateTLockX
# Name                          |Descr         |Parameters                              |Source                                                                          
P=_1sp_RG4631_TLockX            |EscalateTLockX|                                        |set nocount on declare @i integer select @i=1 from RG4631(TABLOCKX HOLDLOCK) where 0=1
#
#===============================================================================
#==TABLE no 658    : Регистр ПеремещаемыйРезервЗакрытие
# Name    |Descr                         |SQLTableNam|RecordLock
T=RG4631  |Регистр ПеремещаемыйРезервЗакр|RG4631     |          
#-----Fields-------
# Name                  |Descr               |Type|Length|Precision
F=PERIOD                |Period Registr      |D   |0     |0        
F=SP4626                |(P)Склад            |C   |9     |0        
F=SP4627                |(P)Документ         |C   |9     |0        
F=SP4628                |(P)Товар            |C   |9     |0        
F=SP4629                |(P)Единица          |C   |9     |0        
F=SP4630                |(P)Количество       |N   |14    |3        
#----Indexes------
# Name                           |Descr         |Unique|Indexed fields                                              |Type       
I=PK_RG4631                      |PERIOD+PROP   |1     |PERIOD,SP4626,SP4627,SP4628,SP4629                          |1          
#
#===============================================================================
#==PROCEDURE 
# Name                          |Descr         |Parameters                              |Source                                                                          
P=_1sp_RG4631_Change            |              |@per D,@p1 C(9),@p2 C(9),@p3 C(9),@p4 C(9),@p5 N(14,3)|{\
Set Nocount On
Update RG4631
  set SP4630=Case When ABS(SP4630+@p5)>99999999999.999 Then 99999999999.999 Else SP4630+@p5 End
  where PERIOD=@per AND SP4626=@p1 AND SP4627=@p2 AND SP4628=@p3 AND SP4629=@p4
if @@ROWCOUNT=0
    insert into RG4631 values(@per,@p1,@p2,@p3,@p4,@p5)
\}
