# Name                          |Descr         |Parameters                              |Source                                                                          
P=_1sp_RA5141_TLock             |EscalateTLock |                                        |set nocount on declare @i integer select @i=1 from RA5141(TABLOCK HOLDLOCK) where 0=1
#
#===============================================================================
#==PROCEDURE EscalateTLockX
# Name                          |Descr         |Parameters                              |Source                                                                          
P=_1sp_RA5141_TLockX            |EscalateTLockX|                                        |set nocount on declare @i integer select @i=1 from RA5141(TABLOCKX HOLDLOCK) where 0=1
#
#===============================================================================
#==TABLE no 667    : Регистр (Дв.) СостояниеПеремещений
# Name    |Descr                         |SQLTableNam|RecordLock
T=RA5141  |Регистр (Дв.) СостояниеПеремещ|RA5141     |          
#-----Fields-------
# Name                  |Descr               |Type|Length|Precision
F=IDDOC                 |ID Document's       |C   |9     |0        
F=LINENO_               |LineNo              |S   |0     |0        
F=ACTNO                 |Action No           |I   |0     |0        
F=DEBKRED               |Flag Debet/Kredit   |L   |0     |0        
F=SP5137                |(P)Товар            |C   |9     |0        
F=SP5138                |(P)СкладПолучатель  |C   |9     |0        
F=SP5139                |(P)Перемещение      |C   |9     |0        
F=SP5140                |(P)Количество       |N   |14    |3        
F=SP6764                |(P)КоличествоРез    |N   |14    |3        
#----Indexes------
# Name                           |Descr         |Unique|Indexed fields                                              |Type       
I=PK_RA5141                      |of IDDOC+LineN|1     |IDDOC,LINENO_,ACTNO                                         |1          
#
#===============================================================================
#==PROCEDURE 
# Name                          |Descr         |Parameters                              |Source                                                                          
P=_1sp_RA5141_ClearRecalcDocActs|              |@IdDoc C(9), @DocDate D, @CurPeriod D, @RepeatToTM I, @SaveTurnsWithMonth I, @Direct I|{\
SET NOCOUNT ON
DECLARE @PeriodTA datetime, @Period datetime, @SnapShotPeriod char, @DebetCredit BIT
DECLARE @p0 CHAR(9), @p1 CHAR(9), @p2 CHAR(9), @f0 NUMERIC(14, 3), @f1 NUMERIC(14, 3)
SELECT @PeriodTA=CURDATE, @SnapShotPeriod=SNAPSHPER FROM _1SSYSTEM
DECLARE Cur_RA5141 CURSOR FOR SELECT DEBKRED, SP5137, SP5138, SP5139, SP5140, SP6764  FROM RA5141 WHERE IDDOC=@IdDoc
OPEN Cur_RA5141
FETCH NEXT FROM Cur_RA5141 INTO @DebetCredit, @p0, @p1, @p2, @f0, @f1
WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS=0 BEGIN

    IF @DebetCredit<>@Direct
        SELECT @f0=-@f0, @f1=-@f1
    IF @RepeatToTM=1 BEGIN
        SELECT @Period=@CurPeriod
        WHILE @Period<=@PeriodTA BEGIN
            EXECUTE _1sp_RG5141_Change @Period, @p0, @p1, @p2, @f0, @f1
            EXECUTE _1sp_GetNextPeriod @Period, @SnapShotPeriod, @Period OUTPUT
        END
    END
    ELSE
        EXECUTE _1sp_RG5141_Change @CurPeriod, @p0, @p1, @p2, @f0, @f1
    IF @SaveTurnsWithMonth=1 BEGIN
        EXECUTE _1sp_GetBeginOfPeriod @DocDate, 'M', @Period OUTPUT
        EXECUTE _1sp_RG5141_Change @Period, @p0, @p1, @p2, @f0, @f1
    END

    FETCH NEXT FROM Cur_RA5141 INTO @DebetCredit, @p0, @p1, @p2, @f0, @f1
END
CLOSE Cur_RA5141
DEALLOCATE Cur_RA5141
\}
#
#===============================================================================
#==PROCEDURE 
