#----Indexes------
# Name                           |Descr         |Unique|Indexed fields                                              |Type       
I=PK_RG5865                      |PERIOD+PROP   |1     |PERIOD,SP5858,SP5859,SP5860,SP5861,SP5862                   |1          
I=VIA5859                        |VIA5859       |0     |PERIOD,SP5859                                               |0          
I=VIA5860                        |VIA5860       |0     |PERIOD,SP5860                                               |0          
#
