P=_1sp_RG7944_Change            |              |@per D,@p1 C(13),@p2 C(9),@p3 C(13),@p4 N(14,3)|{\
Set Nocount On
Update RG7944
  set SP7943=Case When ABS(SP7943+@p4)>99999999999.999 Then 99999999999.999 Else SP7943+@p4 End
  where PERIOD=@per AND SP7941=@p1 AND SP7942=@p2 AND SP7954=@p3
if @@ROWCOUNT=0
    insert into RG7944 values(@per,@p1,@p2,@p3,@p4)
\}
