P=_1sp_RG11625_Change           |              |@per D,@p1 C(9),@p2 C(9),@p3 C(9),@p4 N(14,4)|{\
Set Nocount On
Update RG11625
  set SP11629=Case When ABS(SP11629+@p4)>9999999999.9999 Then 9999999999.9999 Else SP11629+@p4 End
  where PERIOD=@per AND SP11626=@p1 AND SP11627=@p2 AND SP11628=@p3
if @@ROWCOUNT=0
    insert into RG11625 values(@per,@p1,@p2,@p3,@p4)
